title: UEFA Champions League predictor
description: A side machine learning project to predict the outcome of 2019-20 UEFA Champion's League using classification algorithms. I predicted the outcome of top 8 teams in the competition based on their last 5 years group state performances.

title: Microsoft Teams Attendance Bot
description: A smart bot which will attend classes on Microsoft Teams for you. It's a really simple application which uses web automation to attend a call on Microsoft Teams and these calls can be scheduled using a CSV file.
